00033 static string XMLChToString(const XMLCh* const c1)
00034 {
00035         string s;
00036         int i=0;
00037         while (c1[i] != 0)
00038         {
00039                 s += (char)c1[i];
00040                 ++i;
00041         }
00042         return s;
00043 }

00050 static bool operator==(const XMLCh* const &c1, wstring c2)
00051 {
00052         if (c2.length() != XMLString::stringLen(c1))
00053                 return false;
00054         for (int i=0; i<(int)c2.length(); i++)
00055         {
00056                 if (c2[i] != c1[i])
00057                         return false;

00102  * Back up the current element.
00103  */
00104 void SAXArrayHandlers::MoveCurrentElementBack(const XMLCh* const name)
00105 {
00106         if (name == 0)
00107                 return;
00108         
00109         if ((currentElement == BIOSOURCE_PROPERTYSETS_ASSNLIST_NAMEVALUETYPE ||
00110                           currentElement == EXPERIMENT_PROPERTYSETS_ASSNLIST_NAMEVALUETYPE) && levelsDeep > 0)
00111         {
00112                 --levelsDeep;
00113         }
00114         
00115         else if (name == BIOMATERIAL_PACKAGE_ELEMENT)
00116                 currentElement = DTT_ARRAY_FILE;
00117 
00118         else if (name == BIOMATERIAL_ASSNLIST_ELEMENT)
00119                 currentElement = BIOMATERIAL_PACKAGE;
00120 
00121         else if (name == BIOSOURCE_ELEMENT)
00122                 currentElement = BIOMATERIAL_ASSNLIST;
00123 
00124         else if (name == PROPERTYSETS_ASSNLIST_ELEMENT && currentElement == BIOSOURCE_PROPERTYSETS_ASSNLIST)
00125                 currentElement = BIOSOURCE;
00126 
00127         else if (name == NAME_VALUE_TYPE_ELEMENT && currentElement == BIOSOURCE_PROPERTYSETS_ASSNLIST_NAMEVALUETYPE)
00128                 currentElement = BIOSOURCE_PROPERTYSETS_ASSNLIST;
00129 
00130         else if (name == CHARACTERISTICS_ASSNLIST_ELEMENT && currentElement == BIOSOURCE_CHARACTERISTICS_ASSNLIST)
00131                 currentElement = BIOSOURCE;
00132 
00133         else if (name == ONTOLOGY_ENTRY_ELEMENT && currentElement == BIOSOURCE_CHARACTERISTICS_ASSNLIST_ONTOLOGY)
00134                 currentElement = BIOSOURCE_CHARACTERISTICS_ASSNLIST;
00135 
00136         else if (name == MATERIAL_TYPE_ASSN_ELEMENT && currentElement == BIOSOURCE_MATERIALTYPE_ASSNLIST)
00137                 currentElement = BIOSOURCE;
00138 
00139         else if (name == ONTOLOGY_ENTRY_ELEMENT && currentElement == BIOSOURCE_MATERIALTYPE_ASSNLIST_ONTOLOGY)
00140                 currentElement = BIOSOURCE_MATERIALTYPE_ASSNLIST;
00141 
00142         else if (name == EXPERIMENT_PACKAGE_ELEMENT)
00143                 currentElement = DTT_ARRAY_FILE;
00144 
00145         else if (name == EXPERIMENT_ASSNLIST_ELEMENT)
00146                 currentElement = EXPERIMENT_PACKAGE;
00147 
00148         else if (name == EXPERIMENT_ELEMENT)
00149                 currentElement = EXPERIMENT_ASSNLIST;
00150 
00151         else if (name == PROPERTYSETS_ASSNLIST_ELEMENT && currentElement == EXPERIMENT_PROPERTYSETS_ASSNLIST)
00152                 currentElement = EXPERIMENT;
00153 
00154         else if (name == NAME_VALUE_TYPE_ELEMENT && currentElement == EXPERIMENT_PROPERTYSETS_ASSNLIST_NAMEVALUETYPE)
00155                 currentElement = EXPERIMENT_PROPERTYSETS_ASSNLIST;
00156 
00157         else if (name == ARRAY_DESIGN_PACKAGE_ELEMENT)
00158                 currentElement = DTT_ARRAY_FILE;
00159 
00160         else if (name == ARRAY_DESIGN_ASSNLIST_ELEMENT)
00161                 currentElement = ARRAY_DESIGN_PACKAGE;

00164                 currentElement = ARRAY_DESIGN_ASSNLIST;

00200                 currentElement = BIOSOURCE_MATERIALTYPE_ASSNLIST_ONTOLOGY;
00201 
00202         else if (name == EXPERIMENT_PACKAGE_ELEMENT)
00203                 currentElement = EXPERIMENT_PACKAGE;
00204 
00205         else if (name == EXPERIMENT_ASSNLIST_ELEMENT)
00206                 currentElement = EXPERIMENT_ASSNLIST;
00207 
00208         else if (name == EXPERIMENT_ELEMENT)
00209                 currentElement = EXPERIMENT;
00210 
00211         else if (name == PROPERTYSETS_ASSNLIST_ELEMENT && currentElement == EXPERIMENT)
00212                 currentElement = EXPERIMENT_PROPERTYSETS_ASSNLIST;
00213 
00214         else if (name == NAME_VALUE_TYPE_ELEMENT && currentElement == EXPERIMENT_PROPERTYSETS_ASSNLIST)
00215                 currentElement = EXPERIMENT_PROPERTYSETS_ASSNLIST_NAMEVALUETYPE;

00217         else if (name == ARRAY_DESIGN_PACKAGE_ELEMENT)
00218                 currentElement = ARRAY_DESIGN_PACKAGE;
00219 
00220         else if (name == ARRAY_DESIGN_ASSNLIST_ELEMENT)
00221                 currentElement = ARRAY_DESIGN_ASSNLIST;
00222 
00223         else if (name == PHYSICAL_ARRAY_DESIGN_ELEMENT)
00224                 currentElement = PHYSICAL_ARRAY_DESIGN;

00226         else if (currentElement == BIOSOURCE_PROPERTYSETS_ASSNLIST_NAMEVALUETYPE ||
00227                         currentElement == EXPERIMENT_PROPERTYSETS_ASSNLIST_NAMEVALUETYPE)
00228         {
00229                 ++levelsDeep;
00230                 return false;

00233         else
00234                 return false;

00239 /*
00240  * Set the current element based on the name and the current element.
00241  * Based on the current element, store the data in the array object.
00242  */
00243 void SAXArrayHandlers::startElement(const XMLCh* const name, AttributeList&  attributes)
00244 {
00245         if (MoveCurrentElementForward(name) == false)
00246                 return;
00247 
00248         switch (currentElement)
00249         {
00250         case EXPERIMENT:
00251                 StoreExperimentNameAttribute(attributes);
00252                 break;
00253 
00254         case BIOSOURCE:
00255                 StoreSampleNameAttribute(attributes);
00256                 break;
00257 
00258         case BIOSOURCE_PROPERTYSETS_ASSNLIST_NAMEVALUETYPE:
00259         case EXPERIMENT_PROPERTYSETS_ASSNLIST_NAMEVALUETYPE:
00260                 StoreNameValueAttributes(attributes);
00261                 break;
00262 
00263         case BIOSOURCE_MATERIALTYPE_ASSNLIST_ONTOLOGY:
00264                 StoreSampleTypeAttribute(attributes);
00265                 break;
00266 
00267         case BIOSOURCE_CHARACTERISTICS_ASSNLIST_ONTOLOGY:
00268                 StoreSampleProjectAttribute(attributes);
00269                 break;
00270 
00271         case PHYSICAL_ARRAY_DESIGN:
00272                 StoreArrayType(attributes);
00273                 break;
00274 
00275         default:
00276                 break;
00277         }
00278 }

00372 /*
00373  * Stores the attributes from a name value type element.
00374  * Parse out the probe array type into its own member.
00375  */
00376 void SAXArrayHandlers::StoreNameValueAttributes(AttributeList&  attributes)
00377 {
00378         unsigned int len = attributes.getLength();
00379         AttributeNameValueType param;
00380         for (unsigned int index = 0; index < len; index++)
00381         {
00382                 if (attributes.getName(index) == NAME_ATTRIBUTE)
00383                 {
00384                         param.name = XMLChToString(attributes.getValue(index));
00385                 }
00386                 else if (attributes.getName(index) == VALUE_ATTRIBUTE)
00387                 {
00388                         param.value = XMLChToString(attributes.getValue(index));
00389                 }
00390                 else if (attributes.getName(index) == TYPE_ATTRIBUTE)
00391                 {
00392                         param.type = XMLChToString(attributes.getValue(index));
00393                         if (param.name == PROBE_ARRAY_TYPE_PARAMETER_NAME)
00394                         {
00395                                 arrayData->SetArrayType(param.value);
00396                         }
00397                         else
00398                         {
00399                                 arrayData->Attributes().push_back(param);
00400                         }
00401                 }
00402         }
